WEBVTT

00:00:01.105 --> 00:00:02.705
You're still curious about that car?

00:00:02.785 --> 00:00:03.705
Yes.

00:00:03.785 --> 00:00:04.905
When I went to the garage,

00:00:05.705 --> 00:00:07.385
I saw an engineering jacket
inside the car.

00:00:07.465 --> 00:00:09.225
It has to belong to the Avengers.

00:00:09.305 --> 00:00:10.545
Come out already!

00:00:10.625 --> 00:00:11.865
Where are you?

00:00:16.025 --> 00:00:19.025
Are we more than
just boss and subordinate now?

00:00:19.105 --> 00:00:21.745
It's been that way for a long time.
You're the only one who didn't notice.

00:00:39.265 --> 00:00:42.265
Woo-hoo!

00:00:42.345 --> 00:00:44.385
- Come on.
- Give me your glass.

00:00:44.465 --> 00:00:47.985
- That's it? Scared the booze will run out?
- First glass, you know.

00:00:48.785 --> 00:00:49.665
Let me see.

00:00:49.745 --> 00:00:50.745
Bring it here.

00:00:50.825 --> 00:00:51.785
It's kind of cute.

00:00:51.865 --> 00:00:53.305
- Damn, you've gone pro now.
- Yeah.

00:00:53.385 --> 00:00:55.505
You haven't gotten one at all, huh?

00:00:58.265 --> 00:01:00.105
I've been waiting for this for so long!

00:01:00.185 --> 00:01:01.065
Here you go.

00:01:01.145 --> 00:01:03.505
- Watch this!
- Give me a break!

00:01:03.585 --> 00:01:05.624
Now it's the handsome guy's turn.

00:01:22.345 --> 00:01:23.985
Come on, let's clink glasses first.

00:01:24.065 --> 00:01:25.185
You guys, seriously…

00:01:30.345 --> 00:01:31.345
Hey.

00:01:32.105 --> 00:01:33.665
- Slow down.
- I can walk by myself.

00:01:33.745 --> 00:01:35.225
You can't.

00:01:36.385 --> 00:01:38.665
- Where are the others?
- Almost there. Just a second.

00:01:42.785 --> 00:01:43.985
Take off your shoes.

00:01:47.265 --> 00:01:49.905
Puifai, come on.

00:01:51.465 --> 00:01:54.145
Gosh, is this okay now?

00:01:54.225 --> 00:01:55.545
Move in.

00:01:56.865 --> 00:01:57.945
All right.

00:02:00.225 --> 00:02:01.225
Go to sleep.

00:02:01.305 --> 00:02:02.425
I'll have Time wake you up.

00:02:02.505 --> 00:02:03.945
- What?
- I'll have Time wake you.

00:02:04.745 --> 00:02:05.585
Sweet dreams.

00:02:20.065 --> 00:02:21.185
Puifai.

00:03:38.705 --> 00:03:40.025
Does your wound still hurt?

00:03:43.345 --> 00:03:44.345
Not anymore.

00:03:46.225 --> 00:03:47.865
Someone is taking good care of me.

00:03:51.265 --> 00:03:52.345
Well, Inspector,

00:03:53.465 --> 00:03:55.585
you've got quite the sweet mouth.

00:04:09.625 --> 00:04:12.065
I just had you check if it's really sweet.

00:04:18.145 --> 00:04:20.265
You're totally different in bed

00:04:22.145 --> 00:04:23.465
compared to when you're working.

00:04:27.585 --> 00:04:29.585
Hey, but I like it.

00:04:35.865 --> 00:04:37.105
Where are you going?

00:04:38.105 --> 00:04:39.185
It's still early morning.

00:04:39.785 --> 00:04:41.425
I'm going to detox from work.

00:04:42.505 --> 00:04:44.785
I've been working hard,
so it's time to rest.

00:04:50.225 --> 00:04:51.705
Someone like you

00:04:52.705 --> 00:04:54.305
actually rests?

00:04:56.625 --> 00:04:57.825
Let's race.

00:04:57.905 --> 00:04:59.785
The loser does 100 push-ups.

00:05:01.145 --> 00:05:02.225
Don't underestimate me.

00:05:02.785 --> 00:05:03.985
I was a high school champion.

00:05:04.065 --> 00:05:05.305
Bring it on.

00:05:10.825 --> 00:05:14.945
Three, two, one.

00:05:32.225 --> 00:05:33.505
Up you go.

00:05:33.585 --> 00:05:36.065
The loser does 100 push-ups.

00:05:36.905 --> 00:05:38.425
Yeah, I get it.

00:05:38.505 --> 00:05:39.745
I'm not messing around.

00:05:43.945 --> 00:05:44.945
Ouch!

00:05:45.545 --> 00:05:46.665
Hey!

00:05:46.745 --> 00:05:47.785
Are you okay?

00:05:54.785 --> 00:05:55.985
I just wanted to tease you.

00:05:57.065 --> 00:05:58.585
I wanted to see if someone cared.

00:05:59.185 --> 00:06:00.825
If something really happened to you,

00:06:02.105 --> 00:06:03.905
I wouldn't deal with it anymore.

00:06:05.025 --> 00:06:07.025
Could you stand seeing me hurt?

00:06:11.585 --> 00:06:12.785
You talk big.

00:06:14.905 --> 00:06:18.105
You never know how to rest.

00:06:20.225 --> 00:06:21.345
I'll teach you.

00:06:22.705 --> 00:06:24.705
{\an8}GRILLED PORK

00:06:24.785 --> 00:06:25.825
{\an8}Hello, Auntie.

00:06:25.905 --> 00:06:27.185
{\an8}Hello.

00:06:27.265 --> 00:06:28.505
{\an8}You're back again?

00:06:28.585 --> 00:06:31.065
{\an8}Watch the shop for me. I'll be right back.

00:06:31.145 --> 00:06:33.025
- Hey, Auntie!
- I'll be back.

00:06:35.185 --> 00:06:36.025
Again?

00:06:38.905 --> 00:06:40.305
Seriously…

00:06:41.745 --> 00:06:43.345
{\an8}Ever since I moved here,

00:06:43.985 --> 00:06:45.785
{\an8}this place has been the best.

00:06:45.865 --> 00:06:49.025
{\an8}But she's always leaving the shop
to gossip with Auntie Fai over there.

00:06:51.345 --> 00:06:52.585
Since I'm watching the place,

00:06:53.385 --> 00:06:54.825
I should get paid.

00:07:14.145 --> 00:07:15.505
What are you doing, Inspector?

00:07:15.585 --> 00:07:17.425
It's fatty pork.

00:07:17.505 --> 00:07:18.425
I'm worried about you.

00:07:18.505 --> 00:07:19.625
Worried?

00:07:20.985 --> 00:07:22.545
I don't think so.

00:07:23.505 --> 00:07:25.185
You just wanted to subtly have some.

00:07:26.945 --> 00:07:27.825
Is it good?

00:07:29.185 --> 00:07:30.145
Not bad.

00:07:33.425 --> 00:07:34.865
Do you want sticky rice?

00:07:34.945 --> 00:07:35.985
Sure.

00:07:41.545 --> 00:07:42.945
Stop flirting with your boyfriend.

00:07:43.025 --> 00:07:44.865
Ten skewers and three sticky rice.

00:07:45.425 --> 00:07:46.425
Yes.

00:07:47.625 --> 00:07:48.945
- Ten skewers?
- Ten.

00:07:51.705 --> 00:07:54.505
- 130 baht, please.
- Okay, scanning.

00:07:54.585 --> 00:07:55.865
Okay.

00:07:55.945 --> 00:07:58.665
{\an8}- Six?
- Three?

00:07:58.745 --> 00:08:00.505
Three? Two sticky rice?

00:08:00.585 --> 00:08:01.825
One moment, please.

00:08:03.385 --> 00:08:04.505
We have both.

00:08:04.585 --> 00:08:06.225
Here's the first.

00:08:06.305 --> 00:08:07.385
No.

00:08:09.945 --> 00:08:10.825
I don't want it.

00:08:10.905 --> 00:08:12.865
All right, last one.

00:08:12.945 --> 00:08:14.185
I think you'll like this.

00:08:20.545 --> 00:08:21.825
Okay.

00:08:24.145 --> 00:08:25.265
{\an8}Go.

00:08:37.024 --> 00:08:38.225
Okay, print.

00:08:41.185 --> 00:08:42.144
Okay.

00:08:59.785 --> 00:09:00.905
I've got mine too.

00:09:02.345 --> 00:09:03.465
I'm keeping two here.

00:09:04.665 --> 00:09:06.225
So? It's cute, right?

00:09:06.985 --> 00:09:07.825
Pretty cute.

00:09:18.385 --> 00:09:19.505
Hello, Lieutenant?

00:09:21.585 --> 00:09:22.705
What's he doing there?

00:09:30.785 --> 00:09:32.385
Detox time's over.

00:09:32.465 --> 00:09:33.665
Something happened.

00:09:34.545 --> 00:09:35.825
We need to go to the scene now.

00:09:36.425 --> 00:09:37.265
Whose scene?

00:09:37.345 --> 00:09:38.305
Time's.

00:10:03.345 --> 00:10:04.545
Shit. What the hell is this?

00:10:14.225 --> 00:10:15.345
You're finally awake.

00:10:19.905 --> 00:10:21.425
Didn't you tell me to handle Jay,

00:10:22.065 --> 00:10:24.105
dump the car, and then let me go?

00:10:29.545 --> 00:10:32.745
Let you go film other people
and sell the clips?

00:10:32.825 --> 00:10:34.745
I won't do it again.

00:10:34.825 --> 00:10:35.825
I'm sorry.

00:10:35.905 --> 00:10:37.505
Sorry?

00:10:38.425 --> 00:10:40.705
Does saying sorry erase what you did?

00:10:44.665 --> 00:10:45.985
I'm sorry!

00:10:46.065 --> 00:10:50.665
Do you know how much the victims suffered
because of what you did?

00:10:51.265 --> 00:10:53.385
I'll do anything.

00:10:53.465 --> 00:10:55.585
Please don't kill me!

00:11:04.665 --> 00:11:05.785
After this case,

00:11:09.145 --> 00:11:11.105
I might resign and move back.

00:11:16.225 --> 00:11:17.465
I don't approve.

00:11:19.265 --> 00:11:21.185
We're more than boss and subordinate now.

00:11:22.265 --> 00:11:24.785
Wherever you go, I go.

00:11:24.865 --> 00:11:27.225
We don't know what the future holds.

00:11:28.785 --> 00:11:30.305
Even if I don't resign,

00:11:31.505 --> 00:11:34.945
this case could get me fired.

00:11:35.025 --> 00:11:38.145
No. I won't allow it.

00:11:39.465 --> 00:11:40.985
End of discussion.

00:11:45.585 --> 00:11:50.305
By the way, Cherreen and Tonkla said
Time is a pervert,

00:11:51.145 --> 00:11:54.105
secretly filming people
and selling the clips online.

00:11:55.585 --> 00:11:57.225
People in the gang were victims too?

00:11:58.225 --> 00:11:59.425
Yes,

00:12:00.625 --> 00:12:02.665
based on what Tonkla said.

00:12:06.545 --> 00:12:08.865
{\an8}CIVIL REGISTRATION DATA
THANWA POTHISIRANUN

00:12:15.025 --> 00:12:16.105
Let go!

00:12:16.865 --> 00:12:18.225
Let me go!

00:12:20.025 --> 00:12:21.145
Let me go!

00:12:21.985 --> 00:12:23.025
Let go!

00:12:24.785 --> 00:12:25.625
Let go!

00:12:27.665 --> 00:12:28.785
Let me go!

00:12:38.865 --> 00:12:41.385
We tracked Time
and found out that he didn't go home.

00:12:41.465 --> 00:12:42.625
That was strange.

00:12:47.385 --> 00:12:49.985
It's the same car
I saw at Tonkla's garage.

00:12:52.505 --> 00:12:53.825
- Let me go!
- Shut up!

00:12:57.545 --> 00:12:58.625
This clip…

00:13:00.465 --> 00:13:02.785
will be the hottest,
juiciest moment of your life.

00:13:09.385 --> 00:13:10.345
Let go!

00:13:15.665 --> 00:13:16.705
Let go!

00:13:18.025 --> 00:13:19.265
Let go!

00:13:28.465 --> 00:13:29.945
Help!

00:13:30.025 --> 00:13:31.465
Help!

00:13:36.305 --> 00:13:37.625
Help!

00:13:39.585 --> 00:13:40.945
Help!

00:13:47.505 --> 00:13:48.705
Hey!

00:14:07.425 --> 00:14:09.025
Can you handle it?

00:14:10.625 --> 00:14:11.665
Yes, Inspector.

00:14:13.465 --> 00:14:15.705
Tankhun, how is it going?

00:14:21.425 --> 00:14:23.185
How is it going,

00:14:24.105 --> 00:14:26.225
Dr. Tankhun?

00:14:28.785 --> 00:14:29.945
As you can see,

00:14:31.105 --> 00:14:33.825
the victim died instantly
from a stab wound to the neck.

00:14:33.905 --> 00:14:35.745
I detected the smell
of a volatile substance too.

00:14:35.825 --> 00:14:39.905
We'll send the body for autopsy
and further substance tests.

00:14:40.905 --> 00:14:44.265
We'll see if it's the same substance
as in previous cases.

00:14:44.825 --> 00:14:45.665
Okay.

00:14:45.745 --> 00:14:48.825
Once forensics are done here,
you can take the body.

00:14:49.425 --> 00:14:50.265
Yes.

00:14:52.505 --> 00:14:55.145
Oh, you're here too, Captain?

00:14:56.705 --> 00:15:00.105
I thought you'd let Kamin
come alone like last time.

00:15:00.185 --> 00:15:01.345
Doctor, call him "Inspector."

00:15:02.105 --> 00:15:03.545
Why call him Kamin?

00:15:03.625 --> 00:15:06.865
You never use my nickname.

00:15:07.385 --> 00:15:10.145
I'm not trying to be close
to you, Captain.

00:15:11.425 --> 00:15:14.625
But if you want me to call you
"Jade," I can.

00:15:15.225 --> 00:15:16.465
I think--

00:15:17.025 --> 00:15:20.745
Doctor, if there's any update,
let us know immediately.

00:15:20.825 --> 00:15:23.145
- Yes.
- I'll leave it to you.

00:15:23.225 --> 00:15:25.665
I'll head out first, Kamin.

00:15:35.185 --> 00:15:36.185
Inspector.

00:15:47.865 --> 00:15:51.545
{\an8}Is it true that you secretly film
sexual partners

00:15:51.625 --> 00:15:53.145
and sell the clips online?

00:15:56.105 --> 00:15:57.785
Even your close friends?

00:15:58.345 --> 00:16:01.665
Including Puifai, Jay, and Champ?

00:16:07.665 --> 00:16:09.025
{\an8}If you want to stay alive,

00:16:09.865 --> 00:16:11.265
take the car from Tonkla's garage

00:16:11.345 --> 00:16:13.505
and leave it at the warehouse
outside the city.

00:16:25.345 --> 00:16:27.905
Sergeant, coordinate with Mirin.

00:16:27.985 --> 00:16:29.825
Once it's done, delete all the clips.

00:16:29.905 --> 00:16:31.465
Don't forget to deactivate the account.

00:16:31.545 --> 00:16:33.385
Check the direct messages too.

00:16:33.465 --> 00:16:36.105
We might find evidence
of illegal clip buyers and sellers.

00:16:36.705 --> 00:16:37.745
Yes.

00:16:40.345 --> 00:16:43.585
Inspector,
the license plate check is done.

00:16:43.665 --> 00:16:45.265
The car belongs to

00:16:45.345 --> 00:16:47.265
Chayamporn Hemjarusom.

00:16:55.545 --> 00:16:56.505
Champ.

00:17:08.385 --> 00:17:09.505
What is it, Cher?

00:17:12.545 --> 00:17:13.385
Champ.

00:17:14.865 --> 00:17:16.585
I got that letter.

00:17:20.305 --> 00:17:22.345
There's a photo of the clinic too.

00:17:26.385 --> 00:17:29.425
Didn't you say
you closed the clinic already?

00:17:30.985 --> 00:17:32.985
I really handled it.

00:17:34.105 --> 00:17:35.705
I'm scared.

00:17:39.585 --> 00:17:41.025
On the day Fai died,

00:17:42.105 --> 00:17:43.865
what drug did you two trade?

00:17:45.705 --> 00:17:47.745
You insisted on calling the hospital

00:17:48.265 --> 00:17:49.665
to talk to someone.

00:17:51.145 --> 00:17:52.225
Be honest.

00:17:53.305 --> 00:17:54.545
What are you hiding from me?

00:18:01.625 --> 00:18:02.865
Tell me.

00:18:03.465 --> 00:18:04.665
If you don't,

00:18:05.825 --> 00:18:07.265
I can't help you.

00:18:20.345 --> 00:18:22.345
The night before we went drinking,

00:18:24.545 --> 00:18:26.945
Fai said this was our last year.

00:18:29.025 --> 00:18:31.465
She wanted to prank everyone
by making them shocked,

00:18:32.105 --> 00:18:33.385
so she'd take sleeping pills

00:18:34.825 --> 00:18:36.705
and have me call an ambulance.

00:18:40.185 --> 00:18:42.985
But I never thought she'd actually die.

00:18:43.625 --> 00:18:47.265
Is it my fault that Fai died?

00:18:49.505 --> 00:18:51.625
Fai wanted to play
that silly prank herself.

00:18:51.705 --> 00:18:53.505
No one's blaming you.

00:18:54.265 --> 00:18:56.785
Champ, you believe me, right?
I didn't do it.

00:18:57.545 --> 00:19:00.185
I didn't do anything.

00:19:00.265 --> 00:19:03.025
I believe you're not involved.

00:19:03.785 --> 00:19:04.945
How about this?

00:19:05.545 --> 00:19:07.305
I'll pick you up.

00:19:07.985 --> 00:19:09.585
Come stay here with me,
so you won't be alone.

00:19:10.265 --> 00:19:13.705
Then we'll go see Jay together.

00:19:14.305 --> 00:19:15.265
Okay?

00:19:15.985 --> 00:19:16.985
See you.

00:19:50.545 --> 00:19:53.145
Obstructing police duty is illegal.

00:19:53.705 --> 00:19:57.505
But Mr. Ratana ordered that
the police not interfere with Mr. Champ.

00:19:58.905 --> 00:20:00.745
It's fine. Let them in.

00:20:01.425 --> 00:20:02.745
I've done nothing wrong.

00:20:09.465 --> 00:20:10.745
Care for a bite?

00:20:19.265 --> 00:20:20.425
This is your car, right?

00:20:23.345 --> 00:20:26.345
If you're here,
you already know the answer.

00:20:27.945 --> 00:20:29.305
Tonkla is dead.

00:20:30.025 --> 00:20:31.145
Jay was injured.

00:20:31.785 --> 00:20:32.985
And last night,

00:20:34.345 --> 00:20:35.425
Time was found dead.

00:20:36.025 --> 00:20:37.265
Time's dead?

00:20:37.345 --> 00:20:38.545
Yes.

00:20:38.625 --> 00:20:40.385
Where were you last night?

00:20:43.665 --> 00:20:45.625
I was at home.

00:20:45.705 --> 00:20:46.945
Anyone can say that.

00:20:47.985 --> 00:20:49.185
Do you have proof?

00:20:49.265 --> 00:20:52.945
If you want proof,
I'll get it from the CCTV.

00:20:53.025 --> 00:20:53.985
No need.

00:20:57.265 --> 00:20:58.625
Where was Cherreen last night?

00:21:01.225 --> 00:21:02.065
I don't know.

00:21:02.985 --> 00:21:04.065
She was probably at home.

00:21:04.145 --> 00:21:08.065
We found a car registered to you
at the scene.

00:21:11.305 --> 00:21:12.745
If you don't tell the truth,

00:21:15.265 --> 00:21:17.705
you'll be the sole suspect.

00:21:21.345 --> 00:21:22.625
And let me tell you.

00:21:23.265 --> 00:21:25.825
The penalty won't be light.

00:21:27.625 --> 00:21:29.985
But if you want
to take responsibility for your friend,

00:21:30.625 --> 00:21:31.745
go ahead.

00:21:37.825 --> 00:21:40.625
Time called, saying his car broke down.

00:21:41.305 --> 00:21:42.745
I lent him mine.

00:21:42.825 --> 00:21:43.745
That's it.

00:21:44.745 --> 00:21:48.745
I don't know how my car
got involved in his death.

00:21:50.385 --> 00:21:51.945
Did you know

00:21:54.905 --> 00:21:56.385
Puifai was pregnant?

00:21:59.585 --> 00:22:02.785
How would knowing help with anything?

00:22:02.865 --> 00:22:04.625
Answer the question.

00:22:06.305 --> 00:22:07.265
Yes,

00:22:08.065 --> 00:22:09.585
but it was a long time ago.

00:22:09.665 --> 00:22:11.625
You knew about the abortion too,

00:22:13.145 --> 00:22:14.665
right?

00:22:16.865 --> 00:22:20.345
Didn't you say
you closed the clinic already?

00:22:20.425 --> 00:22:22.265
I really handled it.

00:22:24.025 --> 00:22:25.945
What does that have to do
with Puifai's death?

00:22:28.345 --> 00:22:32.265
Are you trying to make me feel guilty
for not being able to stop my girlfriend?

00:22:32.345 --> 00:22:33.825
You're not telling the whole story.

00:22:34.545 --> 00:22:36.545
Are you hiding something?

00:22:39.425 --> 00:22:41.985
Instead of wasting time pressuring me,

00:22:42.065 --> 00:22:44.065
why don't you go catch the killer?

00:22:44.145 --> 00:22:45.745
Be honest with me.

00:22:45.825 --> 00:22:48.145
Have you and Cherreen
received the letter yet?

00:22:53.345 --> 00:22:54.505
Not yet.

00:22:58.705 --> 00:22:59.865
Well, then.

00:23:12.225 --> 00:23:14.185
Take a look at this.

00:23:14.265 --> 00:23:15.665
You'll understand.

00:23:16.185 --> 00:23:19.505
And please let today be the last time

00:23:19.585 --> 00:23:22.105
you interfere with me and Cherreen.

00:23:22.185 --> 00:23:23.705
Don't worry about us.

00:23:23.785 --> 00:23:25.145
We can take care of ourselves.

00:23:25.225 --> 00:23:27.705
You should spend time guarding Jay.

00:23:33.265 --> 00:23:34.425
Please.

00:23:37.345 --> 00:23:40.465
Or would you like to stay
and have a meal together?

00:23:41.625 --> 00:23:42.705
Interested?

00:23:43.785 --> 00:23:45.505
The suspect pool is narrowing.

00:23:46.305 --> 00:23:49.625
But we can rule Jay out.

00:23:50.745 --> 00:23:52.545
When Time died,

00:23:52.625 --> 00:23:55.225
Jay was in the hospital
with police guarding him the entire time.

00:23:56.225 --> 00:23:58.385
Don't worry about what Champ said.

00:24:00.665 --> 00:24:02.305
There are officers there the whole time.

00:24:02.945 --> 00:24:04.385
I don't want to worry,

00:24:05.585 --> 00:24:06.825
but damn,

00:24:07.545 --> 00:24:08.985
my brother's an idiot.

00:24:09.065 --> 00:24:10.585
He's pathetic.

00:24:10.665 --> 00:24:14.465
I'm scared he'll do something stupid
and get tricked into leaving the hospital.

00:24:14.545 --> 00:24:15.665
Hey.

00:24:19.105 --> 00:24:21.185
I won't let anything worse happen to Jay.

00:24:24.305 --> 00:24:27.625
Your brother is like my brother too.

00:24:38.265 --> 00:24:39.825
If I am not on duty,

00:24:42.385 --> 00:24:44.265
I'd want to kiss you right now.

00:24:44.345 --> 00:24:45.825
Who's stopping you?

00:24:45.905 --> 00:24:48.065
Didn't you say not while working?

00:24:48.145 --> 00:24:49.425
I changed the rules.

00:26:06.625 --> 00:26:09.505
So there are only two suspects left
in the Avengers gang now, right?

00:26:09.585 --> 00:26:10.905
Champ and Cherreen.

00:26:12.945 --> 00:26:16.305
Who do you think the killer is?

00:26:18.865 --> 00:26:20.465
If I had to guess,

00:26:21.545 --> 00:26:24.825
those two are either the starting point
of all this resentment,

00:26:24.905 --> 00:26:27.025
or they are

00:26:27.105 --> 00:26:29.905
holding a secret of the whole gang.

00:26:32.305 --> 00:26:34.065
Then let's end this, Inspector.

00:26:37.225 --> 00:26:38.865
I know where we need to start.

00:27:36.265 --> 00:27:39.105
This place only stayed open because of
the previous inspector's dirty deals.

00:27:39.185 --> 00:27:40.665
Let's search around first.

00:27:41.225 --> 00:27:42.825
We might find something.

00:28:03.745 --> 00:28:07.505
{\an8}MEDICAL RECORD: MS. PAWARISA AIYALUK

00:28:10.865 --> 00:28:11.705
Kamin.

00:28:15.785 --> 00:28:18.545
This must be where Bell
brought Puifai for the abortion.

00:28:19.745 --> 00:28:22.345
MEDICAL RECORD

00:28:47.705 --> 00:28:51.145
Puifai probably had Bell bring her here
because she didn't want Champ to know.

00:28:56.945 --> 00:28:58.545
But was Puifai really willing?

00:28:59.985 --> 00:29:01.625
And was Bell the only one involved?

00:29:03.545 --> 00:29:04.865
What about Champ and Cherreen?

00:29:40.545 --> 00:29:41.865
Hey!

00:29:41.945 --> 00:29:43.585
What are you doing?

00:29:44.305 --> 00:29:45.905
What?

00:29:45.985 --> 00:29:47.585
Don't shoot!

00:29:47.665 --> 00:29:48.665
Don't shoot!

00:29:49.185 --> 00:29:50.665
Police.

00:29:50.745 --> 00:29:52.065
What are you doing here, sir?

00:29:52.145 --> 00:29:55.505
I'm just here
to collect old stuff to sell.

00:30:00.305 --> 00:30:03.185
Do you know how long
this place has been closed?

00:30:03.265 --> 00:30:05.105
Less than a month.

00:30:07.585 --> 00:30:08.865
Strange, right?

00:30:09.585 --> 00:30:11.625
Last time, a woman

00:30:11.705 --> 00:30:14.785
was hanging around here too,
just like you officers.

00:30:15.425 --> 00:30:17.025
- A woman?
- Yeah.

00:30:31.665 --> 00:30:33.145
Did she look like this?

00:30:36.625 --> 00:30:37.905
Yes, exactly.

00:30:38.505 --> 00:30:40.425
I remember her hair color.

00:30:42.545 --> 00:30:46.345
DECEASED, ACID, MOTIVE

00:30:52.185 --> 00:30:54.185
Take a look at this.

00:30:54.265 --> 00:30:55.585
You'll understand.

00:30:57.585 --> 00:30:59.145
On the day Fai died,

00:31:00.065 --> 00:31:01.345
what drug did you two trade?

00:31:03.025 --> 00:31:06.945
You insisted on calling the hospital
to talk to someone.

00:31:08.425 --> 00:31:09.585
Be honest.

00:31:10.585 --> 00:31:11.745
What are you hiding from me?

00:31:14.065 --> 00:31:15.065
Tell me.

00:31:16.105 --> 00:31:17.505
If you don't,

00:31:18.505 --> 00:31:19.985
I can't help you.

00:31:22.465 --> 00:31:24.545
The night before we went drinking,

00:31:24.625 --> 00:31:28.505
Fai said this was our last year.

00:31:28.585 --> 00:31:31.585
She wanted to prank everyone
by making them shocked,

00:31:31.665 --> 00:31:33.505
so she'd take sleeping pills

00:31:33.585 --> 00:31:35.545
and have me call an ambulance.

00:31:36.065 --> 00:31:38.985
I never thought she'd actually die.

00:31:43.225 --> 00:31:44.905
Inspector. Captain.

00:31:45.905 --> 00:31:46.945
What is it?

00:31:47.465 --> 00:31:48.825
You should see this yourselves.

00:32:06.905 --> 00:32:10.065
Sneaking off to see Jay
without telling the police or anyone,

00:32:10.665 --> 00:32:11.905
is that really a good idea?

00:32:12.585 --> 00:32:13.665
Who would we even tell?

00:32:14.465 --> 00:32:15.785
Telling anyone is risky.

00:32:16.505 --> 00:32:18.425
Right now, only three of us
are left alive.

00:32:20.585 --> 00:32:22.145
Let's go inside and talk to him.

00:32:22.225 --> 00:32:25.705
If Jay already got a letter
or learned something from the police,

00:32:25.785 --> 00:32:27.105
we need to be ready.

00:32:28.105 --> 00:32:30.545
Don't you want to survive together?

00:32:53.905 --> 00:32:56.985
THE SO-CALLED AVENGER OF JUSTICE
WHO THINKS HE CAN HANDLE EVERYTHING

00:33:03.225 --> 00:33:05.185
There's only one letter.

00:33:11.465 --> 00:33:14.345
The so-called Avenger of justice
who thinks he can handle everything,

00:33:14.425 --> 00:33:16.025
are you brave enough
to accept the challenge?

00:33:16.105 --> 00:33:18.385
Find out among Champ,

00:33:19.625 --> 00:33:21.065
Cherreen,

00:33:21.145 --> 00:33:22.585
and Jay,

00:33:22.665 --> 00:33:24.625
who is the real culprit.

00:33:24.705 --> 00:33:26.585
Fail, and it may be

00:33:27.745 --> 00:33:29.385
you who dies instead.

00:33:29.465 --> 00:33:30.945
That bastard.

00:33:31.585 --> 00:33:33.385
He dares threaten police officers now?

00:33:33.465 --> 00:33:36.185
…AND IT MAY BE YOU WHO DIES INSTEAD.

00:33:40.785 --> 00:33:42.305
Check on Jay at the hospital.

00:33:43.185 --> 00:33:44.385
I'll stay here.

00:33:46.545 --> 00:33:47.865
Why aren't you coming with me?

00:33:47.945 --> 00:33:49.585
I need to review the documents,

00:33:50.345 --> 00:33:51.665
search and arrest warrants.

00:33:52.345 --> 00:33:55.025
Hey. Let Lieutenant Prai
and Lieutenant Ken handle this minor task.

00:33:55.105 --> 00:33:56.905
I said go, so go!

00:34:11.105 --> 00:34:12.585
I just don't want to take the risk.

00:34:15.065 --> 00:34:16.824
The killer is threatening us like this.

00:34:21.145 --> 00:34:22.344
Be honest with me.

00:34:22.945 --> 00:34:24.225
What's wrong with you?

00:34:25.665 --> 00:34:28.385
You're suddenly stopping me
from doing my job.

00:34:28.465 --> 00:34:30.625
Normally, if I slack off for a minute,
you lose it.

00:34:30.705 --> 00:34:32.105
What's wrong with you, Inspector?

00:34:33.505 --> 00:34:36.225
Captain, listen to me first.

00:34:36.304 --> 00:34:37.784
I know

00:34:38.585 --> 00:34:40.705
you're not scared of the threat.

00:34:42.225 --> 00:34:44.784
Just tell me what's really wrong.

00:34:46.985 --> 00:34:48.465
Trust me.

00:34:50.105 --> 00:34:51.945
Everything I'm doing right now,

00:34:53.065 --> 00:34:54.425
I'm doing it for you.

00:35:39.145 --> 00:35:41.425
What happened? Why are you here alone?

00:35:44.225 --> 00:35:46.625
I'm here to make sure
the killer doesn't snatch you up.

00:35:47.225 --> 00:35:48.225
Isn't that good?

00:35:49.665 --> 00:35:50.785
Make sure I'm safe?

00:35:52.065 --> 00:35:54.625
It feels more like you're here to vent.

00:35:55.265 --> 00:35:56.185
Did you two fight?

00:35:59.345 --> 00:36:00.745
He doesn't want me in danger,

00:36:02.505 --> 00:36:03.905
so he pushed me off the case.

00:36:06.945 --> 00:36:08.145
Danger?

00:36:11.465 --> 00:36:13.105
But you've been
in every kind of danger already.

00:36:20.825 --> 00:36:21.945
We've received the letter.

00:36:23.585 --> 00:36:24.465
What?

00:36:27.385 --> 00:36:29.185
Go home to Kamin right now.

00:36:30.225 --> 00:36:31.705
There are officers watching me everywhere.

00:36:35.105 --> 00:36:36.025
Great.

00:36:37.025 --> 00:36:38.145
No one wants me around.

00:36:38.225 --> 00:36:41.305
Jade, I'm serious.

00:36:41.385 --> 00:36:42.985
The killer is targeting you already.

00:36:43.065 --> 00:36:44.705
Go back to him now.

00:36:45.225 --> 00:36:46.785
Don't separate from him.

00:36:47.825 --> 00:36:48.985
I'm begging you.

00:36:52.185 --> 00:36:53.665
I'll be fine.

00:36:54.785 --> 00:36:56.345
You don't need to chase me away.

00:36:57.545 --> 00:36:58.905
Take care of yourself.

00:37:02.065 --> 00:37:03.305
Text me when you get there.

00:37:29.265 --> 00:37:32.065
You shut me out of the case
and went to investigate alone.

00:37:32.865 --> 00:37:34.065
Did you even think

00:37:35.425 --> 00:37:36.665
I'd worry about you?

00:37:39.465 --> 00:37:40.785
Nothing much.

00:37:41.745 --> 00:37:44.465
I just went to confirm the evidence
with Mirin and Manmai.

00:37:44.545 --> 00:37:47.185
I'll definitely let you know
if there's any update.

00:37:49.905 --> 00:37:53.185
I don't know what reason you have
for pushing me away.

00:37:56.065 --> 00:37:56.945
Why?

00:37:57.785 --> 00:37:58.785
Don't you trust me?

00:38:01.145 --> 00:38:02.625
It's not that I don't trust you.

00:38:04.425 --> 00:38:05.545
I was just--

00:38:05.625 --> 00:38:06.625
Just what?

00:38:13.745 --> 00:38:17.185
Just because I pursued you first
doesn't mean you can do whatever you want.

00:38:22.625 --> 00:38:24.065
If you don't clear this up,

00:38:24.945 --> 00:38:26.185
then we don't need to talk anymore.

00:40:25.705 --> 00:40:26.985
Have you been drinking?

00:40:33.905 --> 00:40:34.745
Why did you drink?

00:40:50.865 --> 00:40:52.025
I'm sorry

00:40:54.705 --> 00:40:56.305
I didn't tell you from the beginning.

00:40:59.585 --> 00:41:00.625
Kamin.

00:41:02.665 --> 00:41:05.705
If I told you everything
I've been through,

00:41:06.905 --> 00:41:08.185
could you promise

00:41:09.785 --> 00:41:11.385
not to judge me?

00:41:22.185 --> 00:41:23.745
I won't pressure you.

00:41:26.785 --> 00:41:27.985
You don't have to rush.

00:41:30.145 --> 00:41:31.305
I can wait.

00:41:33.025 --> 00:41:34.425
We can talk later.

00:41:50.865 --> 00:41:52.785
Even if I'm not a good person,

00:41:55.865 --> 00:41:57.185
please let me love you.

00:42:12.745 --> 00:42:14.185
You don't have to ask.

00:42:16.745 --> 00:42:18.065
I love you…

00:42:19.505 --> 00:42:20.905
without needing permission too.

00:42:26.185 --> 00:42:27.305
Trust me.

00:42:36.905 --> 00:42:38.025
I trust you.

00:43:29.545 --> 00:43:31.225
So? Do you like it?

00:43:33.505 --> 00:43:34.745
What is this?

00:43:37.145 --> 00:43:38.825
Stop pretending to be all serious,

00:43:39.465 --> 00:43:41.865
Mr. Stone-Face Inspector
with a softie heart.

00:43:45.865 --> 00:43:47.185
It's cute.

00:43:47.265 --> 00:43:49.025
I'll keep it then.

00:43:49.665 --> 00:43:51.345
All thanks to me.

00:43:52.905 --> 00:43:55.025
Without me in your life,

00:43:55.105 --> 00:43:56.425
it'd be boring, wouldn't it?

00:44:06.505 --> 00:44:08.305
Then let me try living like you,

00:44:09.585 --> 00:44:10.785
starting today.

00:44:16.265 --> 00:44:18.065
Hey, what are you doing?

00:44:18.785 --> 00:44:20.265
That handsome face will be ruined.

00:44:20.345 --> 00:44:21.305
Why?

00:44:21.905 --> 00:44:23.625
I want to live freely like you.

00:44:24.825 --> 00:44:27.345
Could you support this guy a little?

00:44:29.065 --> 00:44:30.305
All right.

00:44:30.385 --> 00:44:31.665
But don't draw on the pillow.

00:44:32.905 --> 00:44:34.505
I just made this one,

00:44:35.225 --> 00:44:36.545
and there's only one.

00:44:37.265 --> 00:44:39.065
If I can't draw on the pillow,

00:44:40.825 --> 00:44:42.065
then I'll draw on your face.

00:44:42.145 --> 00:44:43.545
Hey, Inspector!

00:44:47.065 --> 00:44:49.185
See? Much better.

00:44:49.265 --> 00:44:50.265
You look cool now.

00:44:50.865 --> 00:44:51.825
This is it.

00:44:51.905 --> 00:44:52.985
Satisfied?

00:44:53.065 --> 00:44:54.225
Totally.

00:44:57.585 --> 00:44:59.465
As long as you smile,
that's enough for me.

00:45:00.105 --> 00:45:01.185
But just so you know,

00:45:02.065 --> 00:45:04.705
I'll get you back.

00:45:05.265 --> 00:45:06.385
How?

00:45:08.585 --> 00:45:09.945
Hey!

00:45:10.025 --> 00:45:11.465
What? Whoa!

00:45:11.545 --> 00:45:12.945
You can't even grab it right.

00:45:13.905 --> 00:45:15.265
Don't stop me. Come here.

00:45:15.345 --> 00:45:16.705
Come here.

00:45:16.785 --> 00:45:18.705
Hey, Inspector.

00:45:18.785 --> 00:45:20.465
You started this,
so I'm returning the favor.

00:45:20.545 --> 00:45:21.665
Give it to me.

00:45:22.185 --> 00:45:23.985
- You want to play like this?
- I'm not giving it back.

00:45:24.065 --> 00:45:25.145
Hey!

00:45:32.985 --> 00:45:34.465
Come here.

00:45:34.545 --> 00:45:35.785
Seon Jae is about to leave the country.

00:45:35.865 --> 00:45:37.465
If we let him get away,

00:45:37.545 --> 00:45:39.105
we'll never know
who he's been supplying the drugs to.

00:45:39.185 --> 00:45:42.665
The letter said
we could end up dead instead.

00:45:42.745 --> 00:45:43.985
I don't want anything to happen to you.

00:45:44.065 --> 00:45:46.065
Inspector, don't stop me
from working on this case.

00:45:46.145 --> 00:45:48.065
Like you'd listen if I did.

00:45:51.305 --> 00:45:52.145
A protection talisman.

00:45:52.225 --> 00:45:53.705
I wrote it myself.

00:45:54.305 --> 00:45:56.305
I know loss could trigger you.

00:45:56.385 --> 00:45:57.905
But I want you to know
you're not at fault.

00:45:58.745 --> 00:45:59.945
I want you to move on.